<p>The question is do you need all of these belongings?</p>

<p>Do your life needs to carry all these stuffs with you?</p>

<p>Most people thinks having expensive clothings,fastest car and latest techie promises <strong>Happiness</strong>. However,I believe it can t delivers happiness and make you desire more and more.</p>

<p>People are living in this vicious cycle.</p>

