<p>Well, Less is more. Right? Live simply and breath heavily.  Consumerism is killing us. Instead of wasting your money on materials, you should do travelling, doing the good deeds. doing charity, making donations and sharing with your loved and beloved ones. You will live more happily and die happily.</p>

